    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      519.22,
      526.34,
      533.26
    ],
    "text": "would apply. In any employment there is a certain amount of trust that is",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      553.42,
      526.53,
      567.46
    ],
    "text": "expected by an employee. When a loss of this nature takes place employer",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      587.5,
      526.27,
      601.54
    ],
    "text": "cannot continue employment of the employee. The only way out would be",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      621.7,
      526.53,
      635.74
    ],
    "text": "termination of services. In the case in hand it is unfortunate that the employee",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      655.93,
      526.53,
      669.97
    ],
    "text": "has lost opportunities to explain his bona fides. Nevertheless I am of the view",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      690.13,
      526.27,
      704.17
    ],
    "text": "that his termination of services in the circumstances is justified. The learned",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      724.33,
      526.27,
      738.37
    ],
    "text": "High Court Judges has awarded compensation. In these circumstances the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      37.44,
      525.94,
      61.92
    ],
    "text": "6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.79,
      526.43,
      88.83
    ],
    "text": "question is whether it is just and equitable to award compensation to an",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      109.01,
      316.32,
      123.05
    ],
    "text": "employee who worked for about 10 years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      143.21,
      436.47,
      157.25
    ],
    "text": "I note the following case law on loss of confidence.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      175.11,
      322.68,
      191.33
    ],
    "text": "1. It has been judicially recognized that:",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      202.97,
      526.61,
      354.68
    ],
    "text": "\u201cIt seems to be that by reason of the part played by the applicant in two transactions which, to say the least, were questionable, he has clearly forfeited the confidence reposed in him as an employee of the Bank. In these circumstances, the Bank should not and cannot continue to employ him\u201d Bank of Ceylon V. Manivasagasivam (1995) 2 Sri L.R. 79, 83 2. It has been unequivocally recognized that:",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      360.2,
      526.44,
      472.52
    ],
    "text": "\u201cWhether the misconduct relates to the discharge of his duties in the bank or not, if it reflects on the bankman\u2019s honesty, it renders him unfit to serve in a bank and justifies dismissal\u201d. National Savings Bank v. Ceylon Bank Employees\u2019 Union (1982) 2 Sri L.R. 629, 632",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      484.18,
      389.16,
      498.22
    ],
    "text": "In Rumblan Vs. Ceylon Press Workers Union 75 NLR 575",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      533.5,
      525.66,
      547.54
    ],
    "text": "Where the dismissal of a workman who has caused continuing loss to his employer is",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      556.99,
      424.85,
      568.99
    ],
    "text": "justified, no compensation can be awarded to him by a Labour Tribunal.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      613.54,
      526.42,
      627.58
    ],
    "text": "Wataraka Multi-Purpose Co-operative Society Ltd. V. Wickremachandra 70",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      639.22,
      111.43,
      653.26
    ],
    "text": "N.L.R.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      664.81,
      120.55,
      678.85
    ],
    "text": "Pg. 239.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      697.09,
      525.75,
      711.13
    ],
    "text": "When a workman\u2019s services are terminated by the employer on the ground of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      720.58,
      525.66,
      732.58
    ],
    "text": "inefficiency, there is no burden on the employer to prove that he acted without malice in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      742.54,
      526.11,
      754.54
    ],
    "text": "dismissing the workman. In such a case, if there was neither illegality nor any finding that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      37.44,
      525.94,
      61.92
    ],
    "text": "7",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.4,
      525.96,
      86.4
    ],
    "text": "dismissal for inefficiency was an unfair labour practice it is an error of law to award any",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      96.38,
      489.29,
      108.38
    ],
    "text": "compensation to the workman under section 33 (1) (d) of the Industrial Disputes Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      118.34,
      145.05,
      130.34
    ],
    "text": "70 N.L.R. 239..",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      140.3,
      309.62,
      152.3
    ],
    "text": "In Peiris Vs. Celtel Lanka Ltd. 2012(1) SLR at 179",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      184.34,
      472.13,
      196.34
    ],
    "text": "The concept of loss of confidence has been well expressed in the following terms:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      228.26,
      525.65,
      240.26
    ],
    "text": "\u201cThe contractual relationship as between employer and employee so far as it concerns a",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      250.22,
      526.12,
      262.22
    ],
    "text": "position of responsibility is founded essentially on the confidence one has in the other and in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      272.18,
      525.82,
      284.18
    ],
    "text": "the event of incident which adversely effects that confidence the very foundation on which",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      294.17,
      525.58,
      306.17
    ],
    "text": "the contractual relationship is built should necessarily collapse .... Once this link in the chain",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      316.13,
      525.95,
      328.13
    ],
    "text": "of the contractual relationship .... snaps it would illogical or unreasonable to bind one party",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      338.09,
      525.7,
      350.09
    ],
    "text": "to fulfil his obligations towards the other. Otherwise it would really mean an employer being",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      360.05,
      526.08,
      372.05
    ],
    "text": "compelled to employ a person in a position of responsibility even though he has no",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      382.01,
      526.15,
      394.01
    ],
    "text": "confidence in the latter\u201d. (Vide Democratic Workers\u2019 Congress vs. De Mel and Wanigasekara.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      426.44,
      526.43,
      440.48
    ],
    "text": "The material furnished to this court no doubt suggests that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      460.64,
      526.22,
      474.68
    ],
    "text": "shortage or goods went missing whilst in the possession of the Applicant",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      494.74,
      526.57,
      508.78
    ],
    "text": "Employee. The learned High Court Judge as well as the President of the Labour",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      528.94,
      526.48,
      542.98
    ],
    "text": "Tribunal took the view that the Applicant Employee was responsible for the loss.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      563.14,
      526.46,
      577.18
    ],
    "text": "The High Court Judge of course observes that there was insufficient material to",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      597.34,
      526.27,
      611.38
    ],
    "text": "pursue a criminal charge against the employee. However the standard of proof",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      631.54,
      526.25,
      645.58
    ],
    "text": "in the Labour Tribunal is not proof based on beyond reasonable doubt.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      665.77,
      526.3,
      679.81
    ],
    "text": "Therefore this court takes the view that loss of confidence and misconduct are",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 6,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      699.85,
      526.48,
      713.89
    ],
    "text": "both matters that relate to loss of goods from the tea factory. As such as stated",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      37.44,
      525.94,
      61.92
    ],
    "text": "8",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.79,
      526.61,
      88.83
    ],
    "text": "in the above authorities the Employer cannot be bound to fulfil his obligations,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      109.01,
      213.58,
      123.05
    ],
    "text": "in a case of this nature.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      143.21,
      523.54,
      157.25
    ],
    "text": "I have noted the submissions of the Applicant-Appellant-",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      177.29,
      526.26,
      191.33
    ],
    "text": "Respondent. The submissions no doubt support the order of the learned High",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      211.49,
      526.52,
      225.53
    ],
    "text": "Court Judge and merely express the views of the learned High Court Judge, and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      245.69,
      526.55,
      259.73
    ],
    "text": "more particularly refer to the written submissions filed in the Matara High Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      279.92,
      526.61,
      293.96
    ],
    "text": "Emphasis is on the question of there being no proof of any fraud or moral",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      314.12,
      526.63,
      328.16
    ],
    "text": "turpitude and there is no grave misconduct that warrants the termination of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      348.32,
      123.91,
      362.36
    ],
    "text": "services.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      382.4,
      526.32,
      396.44
    ],
    "text": "The termination of services of an employee is a very grave",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      416.6,
      526.25,
      430.64
    ],
    "text": "punishment. In the case in hand I have already observed that there is loss of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      450.8,
      526.32,
      464.84
    ],
    "text": "confidence of the employer. In these circumstances employer cannot continue",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      485.02,
      526.32,
      499.06
    ],
    "text": "to employ the Applicant-Employee. As stated by the learned High Court Judge",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      519.22,
      526.59,
      533.26
    ],
    "text": "loss could have been recovered from the employee at that point of time. These",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      553.42,
      526.58,
      567.46
    ],
    "text": "are matters that could have been considered but the Factory Tea Officer holds",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      587.5,
      526.49,
      601.54
    ],
    "text": "a key position in the industry and is responsible for running the Tea Estate",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      621.7,
      526.22,
      635.74
    ],
    "text": "efficiently and the employer is dependent on such an officer. As such the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      655.93,
      526.44,
      669.97
    ],
    "text": "employer cannot continue to incur loses of this nature. If not the resulting",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      690.13,
      363.48,
      704.17
    ],
    "text": "position may give rise to a collapse of the industry.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      37.44,
      525.94,
      61.92
    ],
    "text": "9",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
